{"tid":720325,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"空中服務員比普通人易患癌","createTime":"2018-06-28T00:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T00:43:32.000Z","uid":81228,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"18031de0c6b88a7bed16e1120bbf4a25b5dd4f5d","tid":720325,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T00:00:46.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】不少人想成為空中服務員，不過外國有研究發現，空中服務員比普通人有更大的患癌機會。<br />\n<br />\n美國有線新聞網絡報道，空中服務員會更容易患有子宮癌、甲狀腺癌以及頸椎癌等癌症。<br />\n<br />\n調查人員認為，空中服務員比起大眾接觸更多致癌物，例如助燃劑、噴氣燃料及電離輻射等，再加上他們的作息不定時，令空中服務員更易患癌，即使他們有健康的生活習慣，不吸煙和沒有癡肥，患癌的機會仍比普通人高。<br />\n<br />\n調查人員又指，雖然未有證據證明經常乘搭飛機的人也會增加患癌風險，但邏輯上他們會和空中服務員一樣，會受機上的設備影響健康。<br />\n<br />\n在歐洲，有法律限制及監管空中服務員暴露於電離輻射的時間，科研人員批評美國對空中服務員的保障並不足夠，希望透過研究證明飛行人員所面對的安全風險。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/hot/player?newsId=310967&amp;hot=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D310967%26hot%3D1&d=6o5J3rfpv8I1lZsuW3vT1TANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=940c5ced\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D310967%26hot%3D1&h=af92841f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/hot/player?newsId=310967&amp;hot=1</a>"},{"pid":"34512617b6da50cdf88fb6e4c5deec6abe4509bf","tid":720325,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T00:05:11.000Z","msg":"字宮頸癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e40779081ee284a6d0b7b03d996a2ed56a2a12a","tid":720325,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T00:13:56.000Z","msg":"g"},{"pid":"e7468fb2083c3f6b7a1e0a69758803651ee79a2d","tid":720325,"uid":14623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34512617b6da50cdf88fb6e4c5deec6abe4509bf","tid":720325,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTim